{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take on the role of Blin Albius, the last Knowledge Tracker apprentice, and sort through the most exotic plants, minerals, and animals, in a vast and colorful fantastical world. Unravel the truth behind the great powers of the world and the secrets that rule everything.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0\u00a0</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game offers a rich and varied experience involving free and deep exploration of the world, gathering exotic ingredients from flora, fauna and minerals. It includes puzzle solving, potion making, mapping,\u00a0reading books, learning skills, traveling through portals, navigating the waters, meeting intriguing characters, exploring caves, valleys, deserts, and dunes, building bridges and contraptions, fishing for elusive animals, confronting dangerous beasts, using powerful energy crystals, and many other activities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0\u00a0</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The player will find themselves in the middle of dark rivalries and alliances and will learn the truth behind what the world's great powers preach and the secrets that govern everything, interacting with different characters and factions. The game revolves around a central mystery, its hidden secrets, and the possibility that ancient forces or forbidden technologies still influence the world. Part of the narrative includes searching for legacies left by forgotten beings and interpreting prophecies that could alter the course of the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Are you ready?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">EONIA Revelations is not just a game; is an immersive journey into a beautiful world where every discovery takes you one step closer to revelation. Are you ready to unravel the secrets of EONIA Revelations?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph